Metorex Ltd. (MTX)  shareholders approved a
takeover of the South African-based owner of copper mines in the
 Democratic Republic  of Congo by Jinchuan Group Ltd., company
secretary Olivier Barbeau said at a meeting of investors on the
transaction in Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
